       <div class="textBanner" id="scene1" style="background-image:url(https://hias.tamu.edu/hagler-institute-for-advanced-study/titleImage)">
        <div class="text-overlay">
         <h1>
          Hagler Institute for Advanced Study at Texas A&amp;M University
         </h1>
         <div class="dividingLine">
         </div>
         <h2>
          Bringing world-class talent to Texas A&amp;M
         </h2>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="section--2">
        <div class="sectionWrapper--2">
         <div class="item--1 item">
          <img alt="Dr. Richard Gibbs and associate working in a lab" src="https://hias.tamu.edu/hagler-institute-for-advanced-study/featPageImage1"/>
          <h2 class="s1">
           <b>
            <span>
             <a class="external-link" href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/29696776" target="_self" title="">
              Genetics pioneer completes study of rare Xia-Gibbs Syndrome in ten children
             </a>
            </span>
           </b>
          </h2>
          <div class="dividingLine">
          </div>
          <p class="p1">
           <span>
            A research team led by Richard Gibbs, Faculty Fellow from the Class of 2015-16, published its findings in the
           </span>
           <i>
            American Journal of Medical Genetics Part A.
           </i>
           <span>
            (
           </span>
           <a class="external-link" href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/29696776" target="_self" title="">
            Read more
           </a>
           )
          </p>
         </div>
         <div class="item--2 item">
          <img alt="The 2018-19 Hagler Faculty Fellows" src="https://hias.tamu.edu/hagler-institute-for-advanced-study/featPageImage2"/>
          <h2>
           <a class="external-link" href="https://today.tamu.edu/2019/03/01/hagler-institute-inducts-nine-faculty-fellows/" target="_self" title="">
            Hagler Institute Inducts Nine Faculty Fellows
           </a>
          </h2>
          <div class="dividingLine">
          </div>
          <p>
           <span>
            The
            <span class="Apple-converted-space">
            </span>
           </span>
           Hagler Institute for Advanced Study inducted the nine Faculty Fellows
           <span>
            <span class="Apple-converted-space">
            </span>
            in its Class of 2018-19 and welcomed its Distinguished Lecturer for the current academic year during its seventh annual gala.
           </span>
           (
           <a class="external-link" href="https://today.tamu.edu/2019/03/01/hagler-institute-inducts-nine-faculty-fellows/" target="_self" title="">
            Read more
           </a>
           )
          </p>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
       <!--section 2-->
